description: This Chainlink VRF top 2% rating Anurak purrs with a rating of 88, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 88, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 1 for East, Nine Lives for South, and 1 for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20881-51913-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [88 Votes, Top 2% Rating]
